# TYPO3 testing

- Build the smallest credible TYPO3 13 test baseline first, then expand where upgrade risk is highest.
- Prioritize unit tests for isolated utilities/viewhelpers and one functional or integration-oriented test for upgraded runtime behavior.
- Keep test setup compatible with TYPO3 13 and PHP 8.2.
- Add CI only if it is maintainable and reliable for this extension.

## Report loop

- Write findings to `Build/Reports/typo3-testing-report.md`.
- Commit the report before adding test infrastructure.
- New tests should cover upgraded behavior, not just increase file counts.
